      "para_id": "Q002242.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) When Sin-kašid , the powerful man , king of Unug , king of Amnanum , provider of the E-ana , built the E-ana , then he ( also ) built his new palace , the E-kituš-šag-hula ."
